    "Finally, time savings remain the most commonly reported benefit among workers in our survey.",
    "foot_15 and D.2.3 identify it as the primary driver of increased adoption and reported benefits.",
    "The occupational breakdown facilitates comparison with prior studies focused on specific job roles.",
    "Average time savings from AI chatbots vary from 6.8% among marketing professionals whose employers encourage their use to 0.6% among teachers in schools that do not encourage their use.",
    "Across our 11 occupations and employer policies, the average time savings amount to 2.8% of the total work hours of users."
